Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.99,0:01:30.99,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.95,0:14:03.95,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.98,0:22:12.98,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 100,0:01:31.49,0:01:35.95,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,In SLF, the keys to victory come from the story.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:36.41,0:01:42.58,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}I'd always assumed he was some kind of cyborg \Nwho'd modified his body with technology from the Divinity.{I'd always assumed Wethermon was some kind of cyborg, who'd modified his body with technology from the Divinity...}
Dialogue: 100,0:01:43.29,0:01:44.00,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:44.42,0:01:47.00,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,his classification is "undead monster"!{His classification is "undead monster"!}
Dialogue: 100,0:01:47.71,0:01:49.55,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Holy water is effective against them!{For undead, you use holy water!}
Dialogue: 100,0:02:04.31,0:02:06.61,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, the guy's screaming!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:06.61,0:02:08.07,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\an8}Is his field attack incoming?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:08.07,0:02:11.11,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\an8}No,{No...} this isn't that animation.{This isn't that animation.}
Dialogue: 100,0:02:13.40,0:02:14.53,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:14.53,0:02:16.87,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,I canceled his field attack!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:29.75,0:02:33.93,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}Guess he didn't appreciate \Ngetting splooshed with the saint's special water.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:33.93,0:02:36.64,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Hey, can you not make it gross?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:36.64,0:02:39.56,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,The saint is like the idol of the SLF world.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:39.56,0:02:43.60,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on with Wethermon?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:50.07,0:02:51.48,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,H-H-Hey!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:09.29,0:03:12.55,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,I-I think that thing just transformed!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:12.80,0:03:14.76,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,What in the world is that thing?!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:14.76,0:03:16.55,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I dunno,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:16.55,0:03:20.05,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}but I'm betting we don't wanna \Nlet it combine with Wethermon, either!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:20.35,0:03:22.93,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,An exclusive new form for the third phase?{An exclusive new form for stage 3?}
Dialogue: 100,0:03:25.31,0:03:28.06,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell do we do now?!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:28.60,0:03:31.57,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,A new form calls for a new approach.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:31.94,0:03:34.99,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Pencilgon, go help Katzo.{Pencilgon, go help Katzo!}
Dialogue: 100,0:03:37.82,0:03:41.49,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Wethermon's body has started crumbling away.{Wethermon's body has started gradually crumbling.}
Dialogue: 100,0:03:42.33,0:03:45.75,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}For the first and second phases, \Nwe had to hold out ten minutes.{For phases 1 and 2, we had to hold out ten minutes.}
Dialogue: 100,0:03:45.75,0:03:50.33,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Maybe for this one, we have to hold out until he falls apart.{Maybe for phase 3, we have to hold out until he falls apart.}
Dialogue: 100,0:03:50.71,0:03:55.59,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}I'd say this all but confirms \Nthe "time passes" victory condition.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:56.05,0:03:59.55,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}Given how it's gone up until now, \NI'm betting it'll be another ten minutes.{Given how it's gone up until now, I'm betting it's ten minutes more—}
Dialogue: 100,0:04:00.05,0:04:02.93,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,That's our final time limit!{That's our final time limit!}
Dialogue: 100,0:04:04.06,0:04:05.35,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Leave this to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:05.35,0:04:07.69,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I'll be able to hold out, no problem.{I'll survive ten minutes, no problem.}
Dialogue: 100,0:04:11.77,0:04:13.19,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:13.65,0:04:16.36,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Just... don't get too reckless.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:16.69,0:04:18.99,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Until I can get back to acting as support,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:18.99,0:04:21.12,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,you're gone for good if you die.{one death could spell the end for you.}
Dialogue: 100,0:04:21.95,0:04:24.62,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,I'm leaving this to you, Sunraku.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:26.54,0:04:27.66,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:32.13,0:04:34.00,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry, Pencilgon.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:34.46,0:04:40.01,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}{\i1}Ever since you mentioned the thing \Nabout hanging in there through the time limit,
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.01,0:04:42.51,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:45.14,0:04:47.60,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where the hell is the fun in that?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:51.44,0:04:55.15,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}A boss where you just turtle up for thirty minutes straight?{A boss where you just turtle up for thirty minutes straight...}
Dialogue: 100,0:04:55.61,0:04:58.15,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}What kind of game would that be?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:58.49,0:05:00.95,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll say it flat-out. It's boring as shit.{I'll say it flat-out—one that's boring as shit.}
Dialogue: 100,0:05:02.03,0:05:04.95,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Game design that puts the story first?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:05.24,0:05:07.95,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've played tons of those.{I've played tons of games like that...}
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.29,0:05:14.88,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}{\i1}Games that go for a balance between fiction and gameplay, \Nand fail{Games that go for a balance between the fiction and the gameplay and fail} are regularly given the "trash game" stamp.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:16.84,0:05:21.05,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Shangri-La Frontier is supposed to be god-tier!{But Shangri-La Frontier... You're supposed to be god-tier!}
Dialogue: 100,0:05:28.68,0:05:30.10,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, thought so.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:30.10,0:05:32.14,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a thought when I saw that holy water attack.{It popped into my head when I saw that holy water attack...}
Dialogue: 100,0:05:32.77,0:05:37.53,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the state he's in now, he might just take damage!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:41.65,0:05:43.74,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}A passable compromise between fiction and gameplay...{A passable compromise between the fiction and the gameplay...}
Dialogue: 100,0:05:44.49,0:05:48.37,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}is when any player endures those first twenty minutes...{Any player who endures those twenty minutes gets a reward...}
Dialogue: 100,0:05:48.62,0:05:51.37,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}gets a turn to fight back!{A turn to fight back!}
Dialogue: 100,0:05:55.00,0:05:57.84,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,What, is that your first time being parried by a helmet?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:59.92,0:06:04.64,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}{\an8}Time to unveil the new armor I created \Nfrom Quad Beetle materials.{Time to unveil the new armor I created from Quad Beetle materials...}
Dialogue: 100,0:06:05.76,0:06:09.14,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}Before you get a chance to fall apart, \NI'm gonna beat you down...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:09.39,0:06:11.27,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Wethermon the Tombguard!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:21.11,0:06:22.70,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Pretty awesome, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:22.70,0:06:25.62,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I practiced doing this move plenty.{I practiced the helmet parry a ton.}
Dialogue: 100,0:06:26.12,0:06:29.12,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,"But why parry with a helmet," you ask?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:29.41,0:06:32.00,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,'Cause if you can do it with your head...{'Cause if you can parry with your head...}
Dialogue: 100,0:06:32.41,0:06:33.96,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,it leaves your hands free!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:36.88,0:06:39.25,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Wind Slash!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.26,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Dammit!{Damn it!}
Dialogue: 100,0:06:44.26,0:06:46.64,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,That one did deal damage, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:46.64,0:06:49.56,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I landed a damn crit, and he's not even fazed.{I landed a damn critical, and he's not even fazed...}
Dialogue: 100,0:06:51.02,0:06:53.31,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I didn't go as hard as Pencilgon,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:53.31,0:06:56.73,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,but I still dropped a ton of cash on you, got it?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:57.73,0:06:59.48,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,That money-grubbing bunny...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:59.90,0:07:04.74,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}I'm gonna use the 80,000 mahni I paid her \Nto rub your face into the dirt!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:09.33,0:07:10.41,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Vorpal Blade Tech...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:17.75,0:07:19.42,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Moon's Reflection!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:20.63,0:07:22.55,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Better watch your back, man.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.89,0:07:29.35,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Your six is wide open!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:30.14,0:07:32.18,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Moon's Reflection was a bluff!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:32.18,0:07:34.18,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here comes some real damage!{The real attack... is here!}
Dialogue: 100,0:07:34.77,0:07:36.69,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Assassin Pierce!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:39.19,0:07:43.28,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm just getting warmed up!{Oh, I haven't even started to get my revenge!}
Dialogue: 100,0:07:44.03,0:07:46.28,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\an8}Drill Piercer!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:57.42,0:08:00.25,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}If scars on the back are a swordsman's \Ngreatest shame, then sorry.{If "scars on the back are a swordsman's greatest shame," then sorry...}
Dialogue: 100,0:08:00.25,0:08:01.88,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I'm about to dish a whole lot.{I'm about to deal you a whole lot of shame.}
Dialogue: 100,0:08:09.64,0:08:13.64,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,How did I just know he'd end up in a brawl?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.06,0:08:19.15,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,He's cackling like a madman over there!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:19.15,0:08:20.77,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Is that guy okay?!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:21.19,0:08:24.28,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,I guess as long as the laughing goes on, he's fine.{I guess as long as the cackling goes on, he's fine.}
Dialogue: 100,0:08:25.19,0:08:27.40,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,The bigger of an underdog Sunraku is,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:27.40,0:08:30.78,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,the more his motivation and player skill spike.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:32.49,0:08:33.37,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:33.99,0:08:36.87,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,if we can't hold this thing in place,{If we can't hold this thing in place,}
Dialogue: 100,0:08:36.87,0:08:38.75,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,it'll be impossible for him to win.{he'll still end up an unwinnable fight.}
Dialogue: 100,0:08:49.80,0:08:51.68,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,I tried punching it a few times...{I tried punching it a few times,}
Dialogue: 100,0:08:52.30,0:08:55.68,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,and it's looking like it'll take damage now!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:55.68,0:08:57.31,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Still tough as hell, though.{Still tough as hell, though...}
Dialogue: 100,0:08:59.10,0:09:00.44,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Okay, look.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:00.44,0:09:03.44,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,It's not worth sticking out our necks to beat this thing.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:03.44,0:09:10.61,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}Staying alive and drawing Kirin's aggro from Sunraku \Nis enough to earn us a passing grade.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:10.61,0:09:13.41,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,A passing grade, sure.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:13.41,0:09:14.37,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:15.87,0:09:18.04,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Whip Puppet: Snake!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:20.46,0:09:23.96,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,If I'm gonna be graded, I'd rather get a perfect score!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:36.60,0:09:38.85,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,These two, I swear...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:52.20,0:09:53.82,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Okay, maybe not.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:53.82,0:09:55.20,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,I didn't leave a dent!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:56.62,0:09:57.91,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:58.16,0:09:59.58,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Evil Force.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:59.91,0:10:01.58,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,It increases stats for fifteen minutes!{It increases the user's stats for fifteen minutes!}
Dialogue: 100,0:10:02.08,0:10:05.58,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Even in your current state,
Dialogue: 100,0:10:05.58,0:10:11.72,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,it should give you abilities on par with level 99 or so!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:11.72,0:10:14.01,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Level 99?!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:14.01,0:10:15.76,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,This is a god-tier item!{That's a god-tier item!}
Dialogue: 100,0:10:15.76,0:10:18.60,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Why didn't you whip this awesome thing out earlier?!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:19.10,0:10:21.52,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Using it comes with a serious penalty.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:21.52,0:10:25.02,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,I've used it before, and it was a pretty rough time.{I've used it before, and it was a pretty rough time...}
Dialogue: 100,0:10:26.11,0:10:27.61,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Penalty?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:27.61,0:10:32.03,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,I'll admit, I'm getting tired of this one-sided fight, too.{I'll admit, I'm getting tired of this one-sided fight, too...}
Dialogue: 100,0:10:32.65,0:10:34.78,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,You said you want a perfect score, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:34.78,0:10:36.91,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,So I'm sure you're prepared for the risk—
Dialogue: 100,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.16,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,A penalty?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:41.16,0:10:42.50,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Sounds fine to me.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:45.58,0:10:50.34,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,I'm gonna turn you to scrap and get a big ol' A-plus!{I'm gonna turn you to scrap and get a big old A-plus!}
Dialogue: 100,0:10:54.72,0:10:57.72,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,H-Huh? Why's everything suddenly in photo-negative?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:58.35,0:11:00.64,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,I feel like my hearing's gone fuzzy, too.{I feel like my hearing's gone fuzzy, too...}
Dialogue: 100,0:11:00.85,0:11:03.52,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}It's probably also screwing with \Nyour sense of smell and taste!{It's probably screwing with your sense of smell and taste, too!}
Dialogue: 100,0:11:04.44,0:11:06.48,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Is this the "penalty"?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:06.48,0:11:08.69,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Well, it does feel a little weird,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:08.69,0:11:10.94,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,but it's not nearly as bad as I expected!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:10.94,0:11:14.45,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Actually... that's not the bad part.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:14.86,0:11:19.03,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Every thirty seconds, your level decreases by one.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:21.41,0:11:22.29,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:24.16,0:11:27.17,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Huh? My level goes down?!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:27.17,0:11:30.09,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Th-This thing lasts fifteen minutes!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:30.09,0:11:32.42,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Does it stick around after the battle, too?!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:32.71,0:11:33.55,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:33.55,0:11:37.43,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,I've used it myself, and the sense of loss was palpable.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:39.39,0:11:41.60,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,If it's every thirty seconds...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:42.77,0:11:45.14,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,For fifteen minutes... I lose thirty levels?!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:45.14,0:11:49.61,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,{\q2}So when the fight's over, \NI'll have to start back from level 20?!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:49.61,0:11:52.73,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say that sooner?!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:53.19,0:11:54.44,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Ah, it went down...
Dialogue: 100,0:11:54.44,0:11:57.24,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,You ate it before I could tell you!{You ate it before I could!}
Dialogue: 100,0:11:57.66,0:12:01.53,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}Oh, and I'll use my remaining Scale points \Nto boost my own stats!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:01.53,0:12:02.70,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:03.08,0:12:06.58,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Still, I can't believe you chewed it.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:06.58,0:12:08.71,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,I know it's just flavor text stuff in a game,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.79,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,but I learned what those are made of,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:10.79,0:12:13.75,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,and I haven't been able to stomach one since.{and I haven't been able to stomach one since...}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:14.42,0:12:16.17,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,What the hell did you let me eat?!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:20.09,0:12:22.35,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Okay, now I'm pissed!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:22.35,0:12:25.72,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,You're gonna be my punching bag, you robot jerk!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:26.10,0:12:30.40,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Red plus black makes crimson!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:32.82,0:12:35.61,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Combo Spirit Fist: Flame Crimson!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:36.36,0:12:38.82,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,And I'll max out my buffs.{And I'll max out my buffs...}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:40.53,0:12:42.24,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Let's get to it, Katzo!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:42.70,0:12:44.24,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Infight...{Infight!}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:44.24,0:12:46.16,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,into...{Into...}
Dialogue: 100,0:12:46.70,0:12:48.96,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Dual Impact!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:49.42,0:12:52.42,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,With my right fist, I create a cross-shaped seal...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:52.84,0:12:57.76,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,then I pound it with a right straight punch!{Then I pound it with a right straight punch!}
Dialogue: 100,0:13:00.38,0:13:02.01,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Nice! You finally staggered it!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:02.76,0:13:04.51,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Looks like the medicine did its thing!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:04.89,0:13:10.02,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Now I'm gonna stab its knee until it shatters!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:10.73,0:13:12.98,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Spear of Sunlight!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:19.65,0:13:23.37,Default,Arthur,0,0,0,,{\q2}{\i1}I know it dealt damage... \Nbut even with all those stacked buffs...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:23.82,0:13:25.99,Default,Arthur,0,0,0,,{\i1}I still can't even crack it?!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:29.71,0:13:30.87,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Pencilgon!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:34.17,0:13:35.54,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Sheesh...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:35.54,0:13:39.26,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\q2}I wish you'd be clearer about \Nwhen your stagger phase ends!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:40.30,0:13:45.26,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,{\q2}I guess we'll need more than stat boosts \Nto make a breakthrough here.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:45.64,0:13:48.72,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Its armor seems thickest around the waist.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:48.72,0:13:51.27,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,That's probably where all the important bits are stored.{That's probably where all the important bits are stored...}
Dialogue: 100,0:13:51.98,0:13:57.27,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,But how the heck do we go about prying it open?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:12.00,0:14:12.96,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:12.96,0:14:17.09,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I think I've got the hang of the head-parry-slash combo.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:19.30,0:14:21.13,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,What's the matter, man?!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:21.13,0:14:25.22,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}Are you that depressed that your robo-samurai \Nsword techniques won't work on me?!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:28.76,0:14:32.35,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew these Moonblades were a good match for me.{I knew these Moonblades were a good match for my skills.}
Dialogue: 100,0:14:36.31,0:14:40.57,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}{\i1}I've got a skill I can only activate \Nwhen my HP falls below one-third,{I've got a skill I can only activate when my HP fall below one-third—}
Dialogue: 100,0:14:40.57,0:14:42.65,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\an8}Climax Boost.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:42.65,0:14:44.36,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}For five minutes after activating,
Dialogue: 100,0:14:44.57,0:14:52.37,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}{\i1}it boosts my stats in proportion \Nto the level gap between me and my enemy.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:53.00,0:14:55.12,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I've got so little HP,
Dialogue: 100,0:14:55.12,0:15:00.63,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}{\i1}there's no way to use Wethermon's attacks \Nto fine-tune them down to one-third.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:01.13,0:15:01.59,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 100,0:15:02.09,0:15:06.59,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}{\i1}with the Moonblades' ability to shave down \Nand recover my HP with every attack,{With the Moonblades' ability to shave down and recover my HP with every attack,} {\i1}I can do it.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:07.05,0:15:09.93,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}And last but not least, {And one more thing...}Hunger Wolf.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:09.93,0:15:12.10,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}It only lasts for one minute,
Dialogue: 100,0:15:12.10,0:15:14.35,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}but in exchange for depleting my stamina and such,
Dialogue: 100,0:15:14.35,0:15:18.27,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}it increases my strength, agility, and vitality!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:18.27,0:15:19.36,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Thunderclap!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:19.36,0:15:24.82,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}{\i1}The stat increase is in proportion to how few HP \Nyou've got, and your "hunger" level!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:22.65,0:15:23.74,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nimbus Fist!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:26.49,0:15:30.24,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}SLF has a gauge to represent your hunger.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:30.70,0:15:32.74,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}It fills back up when you eat,
Dialogue: 100,0:15:32.74,0:15:36.25,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}{\i1}and if you go hungry for too long, \Nit impacts your stamina recovery rate.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:36.25,0:15:38.33,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naturally, I micromanaged that too!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:39.08,0:15:41.59,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm at just the right level of hunger!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:41.59,0:15:44.76,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I can combine these skills just right, I know I can win this!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:51.64,0:15:52.51,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}His sword's at his hip.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:52.85,0:15:54.56,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Another Wind Slash?!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:54.56,0:15:58.27,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll block it with a head-parry from Parry Protect!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:00.15,0:16:01.02,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here it comes!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:01.86,0:16:03.40,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Parry!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:05.53,0:16:06.36,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:08.57,0:16:10.74,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,What the... Where's the slash?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:27.09,0:16:28.05,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,A...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.09,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Alice.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:33.14,0:16:36.64,Default,Vysache,0,0,0,,He's an awkward one, you see.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:37.60,0:16:42.02,Default,Vysache,0,0,0,,He's a living corpse, unable to even put himself to rest.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:42.27,0:16:47.28,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,{\q2}So as you face down Wethermon the Tombguard, \NI wish to entrust this to you.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:52.74,0:16:54.54,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Alice.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:55.49,0:16:56.54,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Alice?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:56.83,0:17:03.29,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Alice... ID key... fragment.{A...lice... ID key... fragment.}
Dialogue: 100,0:17:04.09,0:17:08.55,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Alice... is still... known?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:08.80,0:17:12.05,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}This isn't a skill incantation.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:12.34,0:17:15.56,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,For endless eternity...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:15.56,0:17:16.35,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's talking?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:16.35,0:17:19.31,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,{\an8}I have lain here... rotting...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:19.31,0:17:24.11,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,{\an8}I did not... see... their fate...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:19.89,0:17:24.11,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought he was a corpse animated by the machinery,
Dialogue: 100,0:17:24.11,0:17:26.07,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}but maybe not?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:24.77,0:17:26.07,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,{\an8}Indeed...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:26.61,0:17:31.32,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,{\an8}the frontier... has been established...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:31.32,0:17:34.07,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,"They"? "Frontier"?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:34.62,0:17:38.08,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are they seriously giving me story stuff {\i0}now{\i1}?!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:40.50,0:17:44.59,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Let us do battle... Child of the Second Plan.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:47.09,0:17:50.59,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}I've got every neuron in my body \Nhard-focused on beating you.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:50.59,0:17:52.84,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Don't make me think about anything else.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:53.22,0:17:59.47,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,If you intend... to infringe upon my vow...
Dialogue: 100,0:18:03.44,0:18:06.19,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Then be crushed by my...{Then be crushed by my}
Dialogue: 100,0:18:08.28,0:18:10.11,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Clear Sky Conquest.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:11.40,0:18:13.70,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Guess he's finally getting serious!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:14.03,0:18:15.87,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Sounds great! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:18.49,0:18:19.41,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Wind Slash.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:22.50,0:18:24.21,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I thought maybe you'd changed things up,
Dialogue: 100,0:18:24.21,0:18:25.67,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,but a normal Wind Slash—{but a standard Wind Slash—}
Dialogue: 100,0:18:25.96,0:18:27.00,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Thunderclap.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:27.25,0:18:29.25,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Not a second's break between them?!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:29.25,0:18:31.51,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,What's the big hurry, Wethermon?!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:31.51,0:18:33.01,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Nimbus Fist.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:36.26,0:18:37.01,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}You kidding me?!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:37.80,0:18:41.52,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}The freaking lightning hasn't even stopped yet!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:45.52,0:18:49.40,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}{\i1}He's chaining attacks like crazy{He's chaining attacks like crazy,} \Nwith basically no delay in between them.{with basically no time lag between them...}
Dialogue: 100,0:18:49.98,0:18:52.32,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Tidal Rush!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:00.58,0:19:03.00,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,You can do that one with your sword in hand, too, huh?!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:03.87,0:19:04.96,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Wind Slash.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:04.96,0:19:05.92,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,At the head?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:05.92,0:19:06.54,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Wind Slash.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:06.54,0:19:07.50,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,The torso?!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:07.50,0:19:08.13,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Wind Slash.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:08.13,0:19:09.17,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,The legs?!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:09.50,0:19:11.05,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Okay, I get it now!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:11.30,0:19:16.22,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\an8}You can spam attacks without recast time!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:16.22,0:19:18.30,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's pretty messed up!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:19.01,0:19:22.06,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I supposed to anticipate every move?{Am I supposed to see every move coming?}
Dialogue: 100,0:19:22.06,0:19:23.89,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}That feels like pretty broken game balance.{That feels like pretty broken game balance...}
Dialogue: 100,0:19:25.98,0:19:27.40,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}The hell is he doing now?!{The hell is he telegraphing?!}
Dialogue: 100,0:19:27.90,0:19:29.61,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Pyroclastic Wyrm.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:33.74,0:19:36.32,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}A new move?!{A new move, now?!}
Dialogue: 100,0:19:54.26,0:19:55.80,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Black clouds?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:57.01,0:19:58.80,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Ash Blizzard!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:03.89,0:20:05.23,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,A combo attack?!{A combination attack?!}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:14.23,0:20:15.82,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,What's the matter, man?
Dialogue: 100,0:20:15.82,0:20:20.16,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,If you don't get me on the first hit, you miss your chance!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:21.83,0:20:24.83,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\q2}{\i1}Still, I don't have much in the way \Nof stamina or dodge skills left.{Still, I don't have much in the way of stamina or dodge skills left...}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:24.83,0:20:27.29,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}If this chain attack barrage keeps up...
Dialogue: 100,0:20:30.75,0:20:33.25,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Well, bring it on!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:33.25,0:20:35.21,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I'll hang on with pure chutzpah!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:35.21,0:20:37.88,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,It's gonna take more than this to beat me!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:38.13,0:20:39.89,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,And I've got a few ideas of my—
Dialogue: 100,0:20:40.30,0:20:42.97,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Clear Sky Conquest.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:44.89,0:20:49.31,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,{\an8}Through the cycle of rebirth and a parting gift...{Through the cycle of rebirth and a parting gift,}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:47.98,0:20:48.85,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's fast!
Dialogue: 100,0:20:48.85,0:20:50.65,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm already running at top speed!{I'm already running as fast as I can!}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:50.98,0:20:52.52,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,{\an8}I bring the ultimate end.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:53.19,0:20:54.57,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the hell? My legs—
Dialogue: 100,0:20:55.03,0:20:57.78,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,{\an8}With the transformation of "clear sky..."{With transformation of "clear sky,"}
Dialogue: 100,0:20:55.69,0:20:58.53,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}This isn't like his other moves.
Dialogue: 100,0:20:59.03,0:21:00.66,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,{\an8}I deal the ultimate...{I deal the ultimate}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:00.66,0:21:02.24,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll have to take it head-on!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:02.24,0:21:07.20,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll use this helmet to parry, no matter what!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:03.45,0:21:04.70,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,{\an8}...strike.{strike.}
Dialogue: 100,0:21:07.54,0:21:10.58,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,That which can cleave even dragons...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:11.79,0:21:13.54,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Sky Clear!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:29.02,0:21:30.06,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the heck was that?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:31.56,0:21:33.56,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Sky Clear," he called it, I guess...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:35.07,0:21:40.15,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}But this move is way too nasty.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:45.87,0:21:47.08,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Will it reach?!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:47.08,0:21:47.83,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 100,0:21:57.92,0:22:00.26,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's like I told you...
Dialogue: 100,0:22:07.22,0:22:10.68,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's gonna take more than that to beat me!
